Click each name for their definition:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.rhymezone.com/r/rhyme.cgi?Word=aeon&amp;typeofrhyme=def&amp;org1=syl&amp;org2=l">Aeonii</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.rhymezone.com/r/rhyme.cgi?Word=elysium&amp;typeofrhyme=def&amp;org1=syl&amp;org2=l">Elysium</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Aeonii - Was originally going to be just be Aeon because I, too, like short names. But I also like to have double letters for some reason, and &quot;Aeon&quot; did not sound fluid, complete.<br>
<br>
I put a *lot* of thought into naming every toon. Days and days of thought and contemplation, actually. It's the hardest part of making a toon for me.<br>
<br>
I selected Aeonii as my first name because being a cleric, my healing helps keep people alive, and our toons are pretty much immortal. And of course, everyone who needs a rezz needs a special place to wait... (no, not that you will wait in Elysium forever waiting on a rezz! Lol!)<br>
<br>
That is me, at your service.<br>
